714512f-a.text:
34-36 West 76th Street, south side, between Central Park West and Columbus Avenue.
About 1914.

714509f-a.title: Manhattan: 76th Street (West) - Central Park West
714509f-a.text:
The New York Historical.Society Annex, 5 West 76th Street, west of and adjoining the N.W. corner of Central Park West.
September 9, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.

714510f-a.title: Manhattan: 76th Street (West) - Central Park West
714510f-a.text:
West 76th Street, south side, west from Central Park West to Columbus Ave. (Sixth and Ninth Ave. Elevated Line thereon). On the extreme left appears a portion of the Church of the Divine Paternity; a structure at the
S.W. corner of Central Park West.
September 29, 1936.
W.P.A. Photo.
Federal Art Project.
